name: WSOTP Basic Logo Tee
description: So what if we don't have the Premier League. And who cares if we don't have a Barcelona and Real Madrid. Just because we're on the Wrong Side of the Pond, that doesn't mean we don't have any passion about football. In fact, with this shirt, you can wear that fact as a badge of honor. Screen printed on American Apparel's Fine Jersey Short Sleeve T-Shirt, featuring a 100% cotton construction that offers a vintage look and feel. And when you purchase a shirt through the WSOTP Shop, 10% from each sale will go to the US Soccer Foundation to help aid in the development of the country's future footballers.

name: WSOTP Cincinnati Tee
description: We might not have an MLS team, or even a proper fully professional one for that matter, but that doesn't mean that Cincinnati doesn't love its football. And this shirt looks to pay homage to WSOTP's hometown through a design based off of the city's official flag. See a close up of the design. Screen printed on American Apparel's Fine Jersey Short Sleeve T-Shirt, featuring a 90% cotton/10% polyester construction that offers a vintage look and feel. And when you purchase a shirt through the WSOTP Shop, 10% from each sale will go to the US Soccer Foundation to help aid in the development of the country's future footballers.

name: My Team Is From O-H-I-O
description: Whether you're from Cincinnati or Youngstown, Cleveland or Toledo, you're favorite team plays its soccer in Columbus. And though the Black & Gold might have their home city's name in their own, everyone knows that they are Ohio's team. See a close up of the design. Screen printed on American Apparel's Fine Jersey Short Sleeve T-Shirt, featuring a 100% cotton construction that offers a vintage look and feel. And when you purchase a shirt through the WSOTP Shop, 10% from each sale will go to the US Soccer Foundation to help aid in the development of the country's future footballers.
